caption: I'm so glad this bar was here for us before the Rona, and I'm looking forward to when they're back at it. They serve my favorite cocktails, and the meats just can't be beat! The staff have always been friendly and kind and I have yet to find anything on the menu that I don't love. High marks!

OVER CHARGED MY CARD! Accidentally left my card there. Called next day and was told I could pick it up and that it has been charged already. They put on a extra drink and a five dollar tip. Mind you I only had two drinks. I wasn’t drunk enough to forget this.  When I called they informed me it was a wild night and it’s standard to charge/close the card when left.  Went in there and told the person what happened and that I’m not going to argue over eight dollars but to inform management of what happened.  Bartender must be really broke to be dishonest and over charge a card. He should be embarrassed.

Found this place a few blocks off the Metropolitan Ave exit of the BQE. Parked right in front, and walked into a warm, fun spot. The atmosphere was great too, 70's prog rock but at a moderate volume, so chatting wasn't a chore. Put this on your list!
